Step 1 : create project
# crapy startproject ptt

Step 2 : set the data items in items.py

Step 3 : exec
# scrapy crawl ptt
# scrapy crawl ptt -o output.json 
# scrapy crawl ptt -o output.csv

Note : 
1. items.py is the struct define
2.* first page index issue


